# Files gitignored but needed inside every Agent-View / sub-agent worktree.
# Syntax is .gitignore-style. Only files that match a pattern AND are
# gitignored are copied; tracked files are never duplicated.

# The maintainer's private operational notes (session orientation, hardware
# tasks, backlog). A worktree without this directory starts without that
# context, so it is copied in.
docs/_private/

# Cross-ref audit inputs. preflight runs scripts/_research/coverage-cross-
# ref-audit.ts which reads the Ghidra paramnames JSON + the AxeEdit XML.
# Without these, preflight goes red in fresh worktrees and an agent might
# either skip the check or chase a phantom regression. (Lesson from Session
# F, 2026-05-16: worktree spawned fresh, audit failed standalone, agent
# correctly identified as environmental.)
samples/captured/decoded/ghidra-am4-paramnames.json
samples/captured/decoded/binarydata/extracted/__block_layout.xml
samples/captured/decoded/binarydata/extracted/__block_layout_expert.xml

# Future-proofing — no .env is checked in today, but if one ever lands here
# (locally), background sessions should inherit it.
.env
.env.local
